```py
fun double(n):
  n + n
where:
  double(0) is 0
  double(10) is 20
  double(-1) is -2
end
```

```py
check "squaring always produces non-negatives":
  (0 * 0) is 0
  (-2 * -2) is 4
  (3 * 3) is 9
end
```

```

```py
ask:
  | full-moon then: "howl"
  | new-moon then:  "bark"

end
```

```py
ask:
  | is-pt(v)   then: v.x + v.y
  | is-pt3d(v) then: v.x + v.z
end
```

```py
if is-pt(v):
  v.x + v.y
else if is-pt3d(v):
  v.x + v.z
end
```

```py
cases (Point) v:
  | pt(x, y)      => x + y
  | pt3d(x, y, z) => x + z
end
```

end
